rhythms rhythms rhythms is an annual multicultural benefit show organized by sanskriti stanford's south asian undergraduate organization this year the show will feature over a dozen student performing arts groups representing a variety of cultures from locations all over the world proceeds from the show will go to project dosti a group that provides volunteer opportunities for students to engage with local communities in india date and time saturday february 20 2010 7 30 pm approximate duration of 2 hour s location memorial auditorium map audience faculty staff alumni friends general public students category performances dance arts sponsor sanskriti contact sanskriticochairs gmail com admission $5 with suid $10 without tickets on sale through the stanford ticketing office beginning february 8th visit tickets stanford edu for more information download add to personal calendar vcal record email event print use this permalink last modified february 17 2010
